The paper presents a new algorithm for deep reinforcement learning, specifically for tasks with continuous actions and high state and action dimensionality. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), systems and control (cs.SY), and computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV). However, given that the paper focuses on a new algorithm for deep reinforcement learning, cs.LG is the most likely sub-category.
